175 A.3d 164 THOMAS LIDDELL, APPELLANT-PETITIONER, v. NEW JERSEY DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS, RESPONDENT-RESPONDENT.

C-338 September Term 2017

079493 November 17, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005380-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
